articles.title: Build an AI-powered automated summarization system with Amazon Bedrock and Amazon Transcribe using Terraform
articles.description: This post introduces a serverless meeting summarization system that harnesses the advanced capabilities of Amazon Bedrock and Amazon Transcribe to transform audio recordings into concise, structured, and actionable summaries. By automating this process, organizations can reclaim countless hours while making sure key insights, action items, and decisions are systematically captured and made accessible to stakeholders.
